==== ENTRY 2 ====
HEADWORD: Norwegian
<hw>Nor*we"gi*an</hw>, <pos>prop. n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>A native of
Norway.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>That branch of the Scandinavian language spoken in
Norway.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Norwegium</ent>⟦br⟧
